item.title: Override the Digital Divide
item.description: Leverage agile frameworks to provide a robust synopsis for high level overviews. Iterative approaches to corporate strategy foster collaborative thinking to further the overall value proposition. Organically grow the holistic world view of disruptive innovation via workplace diversity and empowerment. Bring to the table win-win survival strategies to ensure proactive domination. At the end of the day, going forward, a new normal that has evolved from generation X is on the runway heading towards a streamlined cloud solution.

item.title: About
item.description: My name's Phil, I left school in 1985 I took up the 'junior' position at my father's typesetting firm, a decade later the internet arrived in our studio and immediately hooked I dived into learning how to build web pages. I worked professionally as a web developer through until late 2010 when for a variety of reasons I drifted away from the industry. Whilst I always continued to poke around with building websites, for the next 5-6 years I didn't pay much attention to the evolution of web development.
